	<Title>
		Learn to say no and enjoy the holidays
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;The holidays can be a frenetic time, with many additional events and obligations. Choose your commitments wisely. Saying yes when you should say no can leave you feeling resentful and overwhelmed. Friends and family will understand if you can&apos;t participate in every activity. If it&apos;s not possible to say no when your boss asks you to work overtime, try to remove something else from your agenda to make up for the lost time.&lt;/p&gt;
